org.datavec.api.split.partition

Class NumberOfRecordsPartitioner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.datavec.api.split.partition.NumberOfRecordsPartitioner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Partitioner

    public class NumberOfRecordsPartitioner
extends java.lang.Object
implements Partitioner
    Partition relative to number of records written per file. This partitioner will ensure that no more than recordsPerFile number of records is written per file when outputting to the various locations of the InputSplit locations.
